<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Booker AI</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .logo span { color: #c8ff00; }
  .tagline {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cards {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #161616;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px;
    width: 280px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    display: block;
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: #c8ff00; transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .card-icon {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .card h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .card p { font-size: 14px; color: #888; line-height: 1.6; }
  .card .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 20px;
    background: #c8ff00;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .footer {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #444;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="logo">THE <span>BOOKER</span> AI</div>
<p class="tagline">AI-powered booking for hair salons & tattoo studios</p>

<div class="cards">
  <a href="/widget/" class="card">
    <div class="card-icon">💬</div>
    <h2>Booking Widget</h2>
    <p>See the AI booking assistant your clients embed on their website</p>
    <span class="btn">View Demo</span>
  </a>
  <a href="/admin/" class="card">
    <div class="card-icon">▦</div>
    <h2>Admin Dashboard</h2>
    <p>Manage all your clients, bookings and revenue in one place</p>
    <span class="btn">Open Dashboard</span>
  </a>
</div>

<p class="footer">© 2026 The Booker AI · thebookerai.com</p>

</body>
</html>
